snippet.title: Skopje - Publisher Announcement
snippet.description:
Welcome to Skopje, a comic book styled first-person shooter with rogue-lite elements and an open world survival gameplay.

Wishlist on Steam today!
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1211980/Skopje/
